doctype html
html
  head
    title Dietary Food Journal
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/indexstyle.css')
  body
    div(id='wrapper')
      header
        h1 Dietary Food Journal
      main
        p The Dietary Food Journal web application provides you with three core functionalities. First, you can add, update or remove food items from the food database. Second you can create a day by day journal documenting what you ate for breakfast, lunch, dinner, and snacks. Third you can review your journalto see what you ate.
      asside
        form(action='/login' method='POST')
          legend Login to Food Journal
          fieldset
            p
              label username
              input(type='username' name='username')
            p
              label password
              input(type='password' name='password')
            input(type='submit' value='login')
            
            p Don't have an account?
            a.small(href="/register") Register now